Ustoz siz bergan url  lar bilan birga bir qilgamman
product va categoriy uchun permission va authenticate larini kamentariyaga olib qoygamman
tekshorish uchun qulay bo'lgani
permishin va token larni tekshirayotganingizda kamentariyadan chiqarib olasiz .Raxmat


# categories
1.texnomart-uz/categories  => all categories data
2.texnomart-uz/category/category_slug/  => o’sha category slugdagi hamma productlar chiqadi,product_primary_image ham
3.texnomart-uz/category/  =>  add-category
4.texnomart-uz/category/category_slug/delete  =>  o`chiradi
5.texnomart-uz/category/ category_slug/edit   =>  o'zgartiradi
# products
6. texnomart-uz/product/detail/product_id/ => productni hamma ma’lumoti ,  is_liked, comment_count , all_images, attributes
7. texnomart-uz/product/product_id /edit/   => praductni edite qiladi
8. texnomart-uz/product/product_id /delete/  =>  delete qiladi

# attribute_key
9.texnomart-uz/attribute-key/ => all attribute keys
10. texnomart-uz/attribute-value/ => all attribute values
12.texnomart-uz/token-auth/ => token authentication
token authentication faqat category uchun qilindi
login qilib kirganda ham token beradi

13.texnomart-uz/api/token => jwtni access token   accses va refresh tokenlar olinadi
14.texnomart-uz/api/token/refresh/ => refresh token orqali access token olamiz.
 accsec token uchun 1 minut vaqt berilgan
Refresh token orqali acces olinadi

